  "detailed_description": "Can you steal the Sultan's magical lamp?<br><br><i><strong>Persian: The Great Lamp Heist</strong></i> is a charming platforming adventure full of secrets and collectibles, with all sorts of cool platforming mechanics - and a difficulty that will make grown men cry. Get ready for hours of platforming mayhem!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>41 action packed levels spread across a huge world map<br></li><li>Fun and varied platforming action - there's something new around every corner!<br></li><li>Secret exits and alternate paths<br></li><li>Time attack!<br></li><li>For the masochists: an unreasonably brutal <u><i>hard mode</i></u></li></ul>",
